17/helga-skittish-seer?utm_source=api", "local": "img/seer/0a0d25a8-4f28-453b-9270-4d449fe0ca65.jpg"}, {"id": "d7bfea15-ced2-415e-b175-4588186536b4", "name": "Seer of the Bright Side", "set": "UNK", "set_name": "Unknown Event", "released": "2024-10-25", "type_line": "Creature — Human Assassin", "rarity": "rare", "colors": ["B"], "img_small": "https://cards.scryfall.io/small/front/5/4/544949ec-1065-46f9-a10e-3e9976ba75d9.jpg?1782727584", "img_normal": "https://cards.scryfall.io/normal/front/5/4/544949ec-1065-46f9-a10e-3e9976ba75d9.jpg?1782727584", "scryfall_uri": "https://scryfall.com/card/unk/RB02/seer-of-the-bright-side?utm_source=api", "local": "img/seer/d7bfea15-ced2-415e-b175-4588186536b4.jpg"}, {"id": "f82a4e85-526d-4456-b700-7760043a31be", "name": "Viscera Seer", "set": "SOC", "set_name": "Secrets of Strixhaven Commander", "released": "2026-04-24", "type_line": "Creature — Vampire Wizard", "rarity": "common", "colors": ["B"], "img_small": "https://cards.scryfall.io/small/front/f/5/f511830b-1c1f-4d30-aa5d-4314726d142e.jpg?1782683212", "img_normal": "https://cards.scryfall.io/normal/front/f/5/f511830b-1c1f-4d30-aa5d-4314726d142e.jpg?1782683212", "scryfall_uri": "https://scryfall.com/card/soc/229/viscera-seer?utm_source=api", "local": "img/seer/f82a4e85-526d-4456-b700-7760043a31be.jpg"}], "flavor_snippets": [{"card": "Wildest Dreams", "set": "KLD", "html": "&quot;I opened my mind to the immensity of the wonders around me. It was only then that I could see the Great Conduit.&quot;\n—Rashmi, aether-<mark>seer</mark>", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/9/f/9fedd63c-22e4-4c36-8a7a-a167a070678f.jpg?1782711520"}, {"card": "Artisan's Sorrow", "set": "THS", "html": "Some <mark>seers</mark> read bones or entrails. Others just like to break things.", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/b/4/b4f38f7e-2369-48c9-9121-4b13c29ea869.jpg?1782713758"}, {"card": "Godhead of Awe", "set": "SHM", "html": "&quot;What she saw crawling upon this world repulsed her. Yet she could not tear her gaze away.&quot;\n—*The <mark>Seer</mark>&#x27;s Parables*", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/7/e/7e34d294-c0ec-4e3c-a731-31b7a29c59b4.jpg?1782716138"}, {"card": "Divinity of Pride", "set": "C13", "html": "&quot;She spoke of mystery and portent, of such unfathomable things that my mind screamed for pity.&quot;\n—*The <mark>Seer</mark>&#x27;s Parables*", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/2/e/2e40c246-276b-45f1-ac86-f15c0df62a08.jpg?1782713610"}, {"card": "Reckless Assault", "set": "INV", "html": "&quot;How will you fight an enemy that cares nothing for itself?&quot;\n—The Blind <mark>Seer</mark>", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/f/f/ff0f568e-4d3a-40a5-b72a-63040ec5402d.jpg?1782719978"}, {"card": "Ornithopter of Paradise", "set": "CMM", "html": "&quot;Through even our darkest days, we must never cease creating. Each new invention brings value to the world, be it beauty, utility, or both.&quot;\n—Rashmi, aether-<mark>seer</mark>", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/1/8/18bbdc6c-b6c9-4f89-8f0a-6266e53c1fb9.jpg?1782732622"}, {"card": "Nobilis of War", "set": "MM2", "html": "&quot;A great siege is a banquet to him; a long and terrible battle, the most exquisite delicacy.&quot;\n—*The <mark>Seer</mark>&#x27;s Parables*", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/0/f/0f002636-1971-468d-b171-7b8147829972.jpg?1782750539"}, {"card": "Overbeing of Myth", "set": "EVE", "html": "&quot;She walks among us unseen, learning from our imperfections.&quot;\n—*The <mark>Seer</mark>&#x27;s Parables*", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/1/1/11bbc404-a456-4a4b-af88-23921d80d671.jpg?1782716009"}, {"card": "Mana Maze", "set": "INV", "html": "&quot;Those who know only one path to victory can never hope to triumph.&quot;\n—The Blind <mark>Seer</mark>", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/0/d/0d62cc17-8fa3-495c-a098-ffbbec89fa53.jpg?1782720073"}, {"card": "Demigod of Revenge", "set": "MMA", "html": "&quot;His laugh, a bellowing, deathly din, slices through the heavens, making them bleed.&quot;\n—*The <mark>Seer</mark>&#x27;s Parables*", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/7/a/7a62b9ea-18ea-4fbc-8e4d-0bacb4e4c47e.jpg?1782751754"}, {"card": "Vanquish", "set": "5DN", "html": "&quot;All beings have an inner light. Let me show you yours.&quot;\n—Ushanti, leonin <mark>seer</mark>", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/2/7/27bae717-56c0-4028-b1e7-a445d6a57176.jpg?1782718338"}, {"card": "Stone of Erech", "set": "LTR", "html": "&quot;At the Stone of Erech they shall stand again and hear there a horn in the hills ringing.&quot;\n—Malbeth the <mark>Seer</mark>", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/b/c/bc02e193-df33-4eb1-adc1-b51ee931218a.jpg?1782697089"}, {"card": "March of the World Ooze", "set": "DFT", "html": "&quot;The fauna here functions as a planar antibody.&quot;\n—Rashmi, aether-<mark>seer</mark>", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/b/1/b1964ec5-0dd1-4b54-917c-cbeab05aba79.jpg?1782687831"}, {"card": "Soldier of the Grey Host", "set": "LTR", "html": "&quot;The Dead awaken; for the hour is come for the oathbreakers.&quot;\n—Malbeth the <mark>Seer</mark>", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/b/7/b79999df-af8c-4724-9631-20eee5a00e49.jpg?1782697235"}], "mechanics_snippets": [], "thumb": {"art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/1/3/13105c88-2926-40ad-bc7a-09d515aa36c6.jpg?1782706346", "small": "https://cards.scryfall.io/small/front/1/3/13105c88-2926-40ad-bc7a-09d515aa36c6.jpg?1782706346", "card": "Cascade Seer"}}